reviewText:
midnight milk party is one of those I can see happening in real life. a collage student get talked into making a porno, then regrets it. a little bit later her take a job at a restaurant were the manager see the video and blackmails her to have sex with him and his friend.

tail of two sisters is another one I can see happening in real life. two sisters go to collage one as a teacher and the other as a student. both get boyfriend that are student at their collage. little sister got the shy guy and big sister got the guy that spices things up.
